{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act47side", "eventName": "未許之地", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "UR-1", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "嘈雜的天空", "storyInfo": "高登派秘書找到娜斯提，希望他們放棄展覽前的工程檢修。經過談判，雙方最終各退一步，娜斯提同意按照高登提供的名單順序進行檢修。另一邊，助理研究員斯凱查封了一家名叫“幸運瘤獸”的公司。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g5_rhinelab_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magic_3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（薩卡茲語）凝結。", "name": "娜斯提"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chasing_intro", "key": "$chasing_loop", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 1.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_labamb", "channel": "lab", "loop": "true", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.1, "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.4, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.8, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punch", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.15, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.8, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punchairwall", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.15, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.8, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punchairwall", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.4, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "密集的拳擊聲。"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咒言在空氣中捏塑出無形的牆，精準擋下瓦伊凡的每一拳，汗水打濕了舊拳套上“特里蒙理工”的字眼。"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "良久，瓦伊凡停了下來。"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼——就到這裡吧，謝謝你當我的陪練，娜斯提。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "lab", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這才到你平日運動量的一半。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是你該出發了。和其他人道過別了？", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒通知他們。馬里亞姆就不用說了，繆爾賽思人在謝拉格，人事科和結構科的兩位新主任我還不太熟。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於小賈斯汀和斐爾迪南，還是讓他們兩個單獨見面吧……", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#8$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣不管是對自己剛從哪位高官的宴會上離開誇誇其談，還是宣講那些能讓一個人成為科學界國王的新理論，兩個人都有聽眾。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說，我只是出一趟差而已。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "需要工程科主任出的差並不多。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#6$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特區政府批准了我們的申請，整合“地平弧光計畫”的資源，以萬星園的技術遺留為基礎，繼續推進浮空科技領域的革新。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#5$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他們同時對哥倫比亞全境的科技公司大開方便之門，甚至為此特批了一整個地塊。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#10$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "進駐人員名單中不僅有煙酒施術單元以及源石製品管理局的官員，連梅蘭德也下場了。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#10$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的計劃書，變成了萬千計劃書中的一份。讓萊茵為整個地塊提供基礎工程支持，已經是他們對萊茵生命這個發起方最大的尊重了。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#10$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "政府官員、科技公司代表……毫無疑問，那個地塊會很熱鬧。娜斯提，你並不擅長處理這類事情。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#9$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這段時間，我也沒有聽你抱怨過什麼……總轄。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星莢已經慢慢恢復如初，但人們望向天空的目光不會收回來。常識被顛覆之後，原本被忽視的地方便自然而然成了熱土。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#8$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自然而然？特殊貸款政策頒布後，三分之一的企業增加了天空事業部門，中小型企業也紛紛轉型，為了搭上“天空熱”的便車不計代價。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#10$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你意有所指，但我對政治遊戲不感興趣。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕一切的發展不是我們所能控制的，萊茵生命也必須做這個發起方。盡可能地掌握主動權，才能盡可能地守住克麗斯騰留下的東西。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這並不難理解。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。那麼，辛苦了。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#6$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "順便問一句，你為什麼不搬去克麗斯騰的辦公室，而是在這間舊辦公室外面加掛了一塊“總轄構件科”的牌子？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我習慣了這裡。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#6$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繆爾賽思也這樣問過。她紅著眼睛，掐著我的手臂問我是不是因為懷念克麗斯騰，以及萊茵是不是總會為克麗斯騰留一個位置。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#6$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來，你只是覺得老地方比較舒適。畢竟這裡的每一個細節都是你親自確認過的。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當初替你裝潢辦公室的時候，你在我身後從頭盯到尾，我一度懷疑你的強迫症比帕爾維斯還要嚴重。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#7$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相比以前，萊茵生命並不會有什麼變化，娜斯提。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#6$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，還是有的，起碼現在員工們來找總轄，不至於總是撲空了。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_896_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……或許，你沒有立場說這句話？", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_896_1#5$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，這也是你選我出這趟差的原因？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 3.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$flashback", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 1.0, "amount": 0.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g1_groundparkstreet_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_tractor_amb", "volume": 0.0, "channel": "f", "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.1, "channel": "f", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這裡剪一刀。對，就是這個角度，這樣主幹枝葉不會受到任何影響。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_prunethebranch", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "測試合格。斯凱，在正式鋪設前你先幫我牽引一下。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_activation"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#5$1", "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下一組。感光性能正常，懸浮姿態穩定，能源輸入輸出也都沒問題，同樣需要牽引。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#5$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，我需要工具箱裡的拆卸套組，等等也幫我拿一下。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那之前的高速螺絲起子還有多功能扳手您還需要嗎？", "name": "斯凱？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看情況……嗯？你的聲音怎麼了？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#6$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.0, "bend": 0.0, "duration": 2.0, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "f", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$holiday_intro", "key": "$holiday_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我真的很想幫助您，但現在我的鈕扣上掛著剪刀，手裡還牽了五棵……樹？實在沒有辦法拿更多東西了。", "name": "溫柔的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "id": "51_g13_seabornnest", "from": 0.8, "to": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g1_groundparkstreet_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，讓我來吧。斯凱走了？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_highheeledshoe_carpet_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他跟您說了三遍他要去浮空層進行工程檢修，您都沒理他。", "name": "溫柔的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛剛可以提醒我。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "秘書的第一準則：安靜地站在一邊微笑，只接收上司的指令，談話涉及機密時就應該自動關上耳朵。", "name": "溫柔的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請放心，您剛剛說的數據和名詞我一個都沒聽到，就算聽到了我也聽不懂。", "name": "溫柔的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想起來了。你是行政部的人，高登的秘書。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#5$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很榮幸您還能記得我，娜斯提主任。", "name": "溫柔的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我叫梅希亞，您也可以直接叫我小梅。我代表高登長官來邀請您共進午餐。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的工作信箱應該是由你管理的？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您先前回覆的十六封拒絕郵件，長官都收到了。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我長話短說。我知道他對基礎工程沒興趣，他也應該清楚我不會接納工作之外的“建議”。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#8$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，不過說到午餐……", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您改變主意了？", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在確實該吃午餐了。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜斯提在工具箱裡翻找了一陣，從十幾種檢測設備和收納整齊的零件袋下，拿出了一塊用鋁箔紙包得密不透風的長方體。"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梅希亞好奇地湊近。她想知道，眼前這個捉摸不透的萊茵主任，究竟是為了什麼食物拒絕了雲中餐廳最豪華的宴請和最高規格的服務。"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而在娜斯提面無表情地打開包裝之後，梅希亞身為專業秘書的完美笑容出現了一絲裂縫。"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.5, "fillto": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.5, "fillto": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 2.0, "fillfrom": 0.55, "fillto": 0.55, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 6.0, "fillfrom": 0.3, "fillto": 0.3, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "68_i15", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.35, "yScale": 1.35, "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "68_i15", "yTo": 40.0, "duration": 5.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您說的午餐就是這塊……磚頭？", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（發音模糊）這是壓縮餅乾。", "name": "娜斯提"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "壓縮餅乾？", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梅希亞無法把視線從那塊“磚頭”上移開。"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也餓了？要嚐嚐嗎？", "name": "娜斯提"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.2, "fillto": 0.1, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.2, "fillto": 0.4, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 2.0, "fillfrom": 0.55, "fillto": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 6.0, "fillfrom": 0.3, "fillto": 0.51, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cakebgflgrnd", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "68_i15", "yTo": 0.0, "duration": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的，謝謝您……", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "68_i15", "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（艱難咀嚼）", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（用力吞嚥）", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳、咳！", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "娜斯提"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以拒絕。", "name": "娜斯提"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "秘書的第二準則：不能拒絕上司的客人提出的邀請，你永遠不知道什麼舉動會影響他們的合作關係。", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你一共有幾條準則？", "name": "娜斯提"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高登長官給了我一本兩公分厚的手冊。", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過我可以提前告訴您，我最先記住也是最重要的那條——", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論遇到什麼樣的困難，都要盡最大努力完成上司的命令，因為沒有人會聽你辯解。", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "娜斯提"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不習慣就別吃了。", "name": "娜斯提"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝天謝地……不，我是說多謝款待。", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實我也有一條準則，只不過比較簡單。", "name": "娜斯提"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您說？", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在卡茲戴爾出生，學到的第一個道理就是：食物是珍貴的，任何人都不能在食物面前說謊。", "name": "娜斯提"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梅希亞小姐，既然你現在拿著我的午餐，那就請對我說實話。", "name": "娜斯提"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高登長官究竟想跟我“洽談”什麼？", "name": "娜斯提"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g6_floatinglabmodule", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2045_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_energywell", "volume": 0.2, "loop": "true", "channel": "en"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "報告！我們這個計劃的核心創意是：人轉酒不轉，離心力替代引力，力求達成零重力太空巡航體驗與品酒體驗的完美融合！", "name": "體驗員A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "jump", "posto": "50,0", "power": 20.0, "times": 1.0, "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“幸運瘤獸”浮空迴轉酒吧，讓你體驗“天”旋“地”轉的——", "name": "體驗員A"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "停，不用唸廣告詞，我只會針對工程方面的調整進行評估和提問。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另一位體驗員呢？展品調整後有什麼新的反應？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘔……", "name": "體驗員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-150", "afrom": "1", "ato": "0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他就是昨天晚上沒有睡好！斯凱先生，我們通過複檢了吧，不用取消進駐資格了吧？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2041_1#4$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雅斯彭經理，無論從工程報告還是體驗員的反應來看，幸運瘤獸餐飲的這款浮空迴轉酒吧都不合格。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "en", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們也很想改善供能不穩定這種技術難題，但確實需要時間……", "name": "雅斯彭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2041_1#5$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照園區規定，我們給了三天。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但研發人員光討論解決方法至少就要花費五天的時間！", "name": "雅斯彭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2041_1#5$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“螺旋槳天堂”的企業流動量堪比特里蒙中心廣場的十字路口，每個司機都有自己的事要辦，但沒有誰會去跟交通號誌求情。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就沒有別的辦法……對了，我們僱傭了近百名體驗員，如果開除他們，就有資金去聘請更多研究員了！", "name": "雅斯彭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2045_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，經理你昨天還答應了我們——", "name": "體驗員A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閉嘴！", "name": "雅斯彭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2041_1#1$2"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雅斯彭經理，我看過“幸運瘤獸”的註冊資料。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你原本只是小鎮上的一個小雜貨商，哪怕銀行放寬了天空事業的貸款審核標準，以你的專業程度，也不適合轉型做浮空技術研究。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而現在我們站在全泰拉第一座，也是唯一一座浮空的地塊上，這裡的一切都應配得上與它並肩。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "求求你，別撕下那張報告單，我把所有積蓄都投在“幸運瘤獸”上了，別撕……", "name": "雅斯彭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2041_1#4$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_papertear", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2045_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就這麼，結束了？", "name": "體驗員A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩天之後，我又得回到特里蒙的高層辦公大樓外面擦玻璃了？", "name": "體驗員A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘔……", "name": "體驗員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吐吧老兄，我們也算體驗過天上的日子了。等你回到拓荒地，吃不飽穿不暖……到時候連吐都吐不出來了。", "name": "體驗員A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "posfrom": "-300,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "300,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g1_groundparkstreet_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放棄展覽開幕前的工程檢修？不可能。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高登長官認為，現在園區的所有研發團隊都在分秒必爭地進行最後的收尾作業，暫停計劃進行檢修很有可能會影響展覽開幕。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另一方面，減少與科技公司來來回回的交流溝通，也能讓您更好地投入萊茵生命的研究。長官一直非常體恤您。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "體恤？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛來哥倫比亞的時候，我在荒地上流浪過幾年，為拓荒隊建過房子，也替運輸隊殺過匪徒。在抓到訣竅之前，我的日子過得都不太輕鬆。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#10$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "假如那時候就有像高登一樣的好心人體恤我，替我處理所有我不擅長的工作……", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#10$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那想必是很幸運的事。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我一定已經死在荒地上了。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#2$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，讓萊茵放棄工程檢修權，一定不是他真正想要的。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您怎麼知道？", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#5$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你把他談判時的樣子模仿得太像，言詞中留下的陷阱和漏洞顯而易見。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是卡特斯，不喜歡往洞裡鑽。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說吧，他最終想達成的協約是什麼？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……如長官所言，您真的很聰明也很果斷。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#9$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那您應該可以理解，雖然長官能掌控園區的行政管理，但真正影響整個輿論風向的，是萊茵。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他不想在關鍵時刻出紕漏，也承擔不起那個後果。因此，他根據各個計劃的進度擬定了這份名單，希望您按照名單順序檢修。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣至少可以保證，在不考慮工程權歸屬的情況下，將檢修流程對各個計劃的影響降到最低，並最大程度地預防衝突發生。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#17$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "減少您的麻煩，就是減少他的麻煩。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#17$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會去研究高登在這份名單裡藏的小心思，各退一步，我想我們已經達成了共識。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#5$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把名單給我吧。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝您的理解，娜斯提主任。那我就不打擾您工作了。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後一個問題。剛剛談判的時候，你遵照的又是哪條準則？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第十二條：對你的上司要足夠熟悉，談判時必須一字不漏地複述他的言論。在外，你就是上司的絕對代言人。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過娜斯提主任——", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高登長官在我來之前，反覆提醒我萊茵生命的工程科主任是個多麼難對付的人。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一度很擔心今天會蜷縮在您的辦公室門口過夜，還提前在包裡帶了毯子。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但您跟他說的不一樣。雖然您不需要他人體恤，習慣用尖銳的方式解決問題，但您總在體恤別人。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正因如此，現在我才能有時間去放心地吃一頓久違的午餐。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝您。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 430, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 436, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}